project_details: An authentication single-page photography web app with a dashboard where people are able to book services with payment, see their booking, and also can review our services. On other hand, an Admin can see all the bookings, change the status of bookings, able to make another admin, and can delete the services.

A React-based web application with authentication. In this web application, users can buy laptops by giving their information. And can see all their orders. On the other side, the admin has a dashboard and is able to add and delete the product.
